# Per-framework leaf output. codegen.mjs emits src/<Name>.<ext> + README/LICENSE
# into packages/<fw>/. The react/solid/vue leaves are now REAL tracked packages
# (package.json + build configs + emitted src, shipped via the `files`/`./source`
# fields) as of the distribution wave (76-05). Their src is generated-but-tracked,
# like the data-table docs — regenerated by codegen, committed for publish.
#
# All five leaves (react/solid/vue/svelte/angular) are now REAL tracked packages
# (76-05 did react/solid/vue; 76-06 did svelte/angular) — package.json + build
# configs + generated-but-tracked src, shipped via `files`/`./source`. Only build
# artifacts (dist) remain ignored for the tracked leaves.
/packages/*/dist/
